Poland sells PLN 76 . 6 mln of 3 - yr bond to public . The Polish treasury sold 76 . 6 million zlotys of Polish three - year index - linked bonds to the public in the February 3 to February 20 period , the finance ministry said in a statement . The bonds come from a 400 million zloty tranche of the three - year paper due February 6 , 2000 , which is to be offered to the public until April 30 , 1997 . The issue price was 99 . 50 . - - Warsaw Newsroom + 48 22 653 9700 
